column5: I havent tied in a long time, but im sure one of these little buggers will attract a fish this weekend. A quick test in the household pond tonight before a morning test run, im hoping they dont survive
Cool Vince. Let me know how they work out! I'm not fishing in the morning, but would gladly head out with you another time!
They look good Vince.  Hope you nail some beauties on them!
Thanks guys, heres a pic of my very first dragon fly Now onto a frog and a crayfish,
